----------

Town Crier is an open-source e-mail templating engine for .NET.

A basic tutorial can be found on my blog:
http://thecodedecanter.wordpress.com/2010/07/19/town-crier-an-open-source-e-mail-templating-engine-for-net/

Enjoy!

Release History
----------
1.0 - Initial release
1.1 - Added markdown support (thanks to friism for code contribution!)
